Wednesday, April 15, 1998

DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

97-1348. In re James.

IT IS ORDERED by this court, sua sponte, that Aaron Nathaniel James, Attorney Registration No. 0039988, last known address in Cleveland, Ohio, is found in contempt for failure to comply with this *1509court’s order of September 5, 1997, to wit: failure to file an affidavit of compliance on or before October 6,1997.
